Package com.motorola.iden.udm

Interface Summary
UDMEntry Represents the common interfaces of an element for a UDM database.
UDMList Represents the common functionality of a UDM list.
 

Class Summary
DateBook Represents a DateBook list containing DateBook event elements.
DateBookEvent DateBookEvent represents a single Event entry in a UDM DateBook database.
DateBookRepeatEvent Represents a description for a repeating pattern for an Event element.
PhoneBook Represents a PhoneBook list containing PhoneBookEntry elements.
PhoneBookEntry Represents a single Phonebook entry in a UDM Phonebook database.
SystemPhoneBook The SystemPhoneBook class was created to provide a single point of entry for accessing the native Phone Book functionality.
UDM Class for accessing the UDM databases on a device.
 

Exception Summary
UDMException Represents exceptions thrown by the UDM classes.
